:

1. *Mrdaj* se odavde! (Get out of here!)
2. On je uvek bio *mrdan* za zadatke. (He was always lazy when it comes to tasks.)
3. Ona je *mrdala* glavom od neodobravanja. (She shook her head in disapproval.)
4. Ona je *mrdala* celo popodne. (She was shuffling around all afternoon.)
5. On je *mrdao* u ritmu muzike. (He was swaying to the rhythm of the music.)